    "title": "Croma Holdings Services is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Senior)",
    "description": "Croma Holdings Services has an exciting opening for a E-commerce Executive at our Indore office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Croma Holdings Services:\nCroma Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Croma Holdings Services!",
